        "timestamp": "2020-12-07 09:49:09.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nhuge refactoring is needed for this chart in H\nThis pod is not used for CI/CD - we use xtesting dockers launched through jobs (internal use cases) or from outside with docker + configmap associated with this pod (configuration entry points)\nBUT it is used by admin for operations to check that the system is running well or integrators for some use cases.\n\n- it still includes python2.7\n- it is based on a full fat ubuntu 18\n- it is run as root\n- it includes GPLv3\n- it includes everything (nginx, robot,.) in 1 pod\n- it is not using a target storage class  (using /dockerdata-nfs/onap/robot/.)\n\neverything needs to be fixed but it shall remain transparent for the end user..\nWork was initiated in Frankfurt by D.Rose but not finalized, hope we could do it for Honolulu..",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
